data.title: Directives Division
data.text:
Welcome to the Directives Division homepage. DoD Directives Division administers and operates the DoD Issuances Program, the DoD Information Collections Program, DOD Forms Management Program, and the DoD Plain Language Program for the Office of the Secretary of Defense.

The DoD Forms Management Program manages the program policy and procedures for the creation, coordination, control, revision, cancellation, and approval of forms within the DoD.

If you have trouble accessing any forms, contact us at: whs.mc-alex.esd.mbx.formswebmaster@mail.mil.
